Package: methylCC
Title: Estimate the cell composition of whole blood in DNA methylation samples
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Stephanie Hicks and Rafael Irizarry
Maintainer: Stephanie Hicks <shicks@jimmy.harvard.edu>
Description: A tool to estimate the cell composition
    of whole blood in DNA methylation measured on any
    platform technology (microarray and sequencing).
Imports:
    Biobase,
    GenomicRanges,
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    tidyr,
    minfi,
    bsseq,
    quadprog,
    mclust,
    ggplot2
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Suggests:
